ADVANCE BIO MATERIAL CO PVT LTD
Advance Bio Material P. Ltd. is an innovator and is dedicated to developing high-performance Bioplastics. We serve a global customer base with design and technical support. Our India operation has offices in Mumbai, Ahmedabad, Chennai, and Delhi, covering India’s Major industrial parts. Our business is backed by nearly 20 years of experience developing high-quality materials in this sector.

Our company has 2 divisions 1. Raw Material 2. Flexible packaging
Raw Material division: This division manufactures bioplastic compounds for films, Bags, Injection moulding, Blow Moulding, Thermoforming, Straw, 3D printing, Paper coating, blending, etc. We also make masterbatches for Anti-block, Slip, Colour, Filler, Compatibiliser, etc.
We make both Industrial compostable and Home compostable raw material.
Recently, we have developed a PLA compound with low melting point and very high strength, which can be easily blended with PBAT and has high compatibility with high strength.(Patent under registration)

Apart from this, we have developed a low-permeability blow moulding compound.

Flexible Packaging Division: This division makes speciality bags, Films for liquid packaging, films for lamination, and Laminates with High barrier.
We have developed high-barrier flexible packaging laminates and fully compostable.
